text.section:
Within the limitations of this subtitle, the articles of incorporation or bylaws of a consumer cooperative shall contain:
The name of the cooperative, which shall include the word "cooperative" or the abbreviation "co-op";
The name, address, and state of residence of each incorporator;
A statement of the purposes of the cooperative;
The address of its principal office in the State; and
The name and address of its resident agent in the State.
